acqinfo.head: Acquisition Information
acqinfo.p: Transferred from the Office of the Secretary of the Commonwealth, 18 May 1939.

bioghist.head: Biographical Information
bioghist.p: Governor E. Lee Trinkle was born

scopecontent.head: Scope and Content
scopecontent.p: Governor E. Lee Trinkle Executive Papers, 1922-1926, are organized into two series. Series have been designated for Subject Files and Extraditions and Pardons.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: This collection is arranged into the following series:
